snippet: Andy Murray has been the standout performer on clay for the past 12 months but world number one Novak Djokovic will be favorite to complete his set of grand slams at this year's French Open....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray has been the standout performer on clay for the past 12 months but world number one Novak Djokovic will be favorite to complete his set of grand slams at this year's French Open.

headline.print_headline: Murray the Form Player but Djokovic the Man to Beat in Paris
headline.main: Murray the Form Player but Djokovic the Man to Beat in Paris
